==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hollander
<hw>Hol"land*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>A native or one of the people of Holland; a Dutchman.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A very hard, semi-glazed, green or dark brown brick,
which will not absorb water; -- called also, <altname>Dutch
clinker</altname>.</def> <rj><au>Wagner.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hollandish</ent>⟦br⟧
